Package: airis.analytics
Title: AIRIS Log Analysis and Anomaly Detection
Version: 0.1.0
Author: AIRIS Team
Maintainer: AIRIS Team <airis@kageos.dev>
Description: Parses AIRIS CLI logs, summarizes errors and warnings,
  detects anomalous log patterns, generates CI failure reports,
  and exports JSON/CSV summaries for the AIRIS CLI dashboard.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
